---
/**
 * Final CTA Section
 *
 * User problem: "OK, I'm convinced. How do I start?"
 * Goal: Final conversion push before footer. Clear, single action.
 * Visual: Centered, minimal. Brand uses typography + spacing, not gradient.
 */
---

<section class="bg-primary-900">
  <div class="container-page py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-h2 text-white text-balance">
        Siap Memesan Layanan Profesional?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-body-lg text-primary-200 text-pretty">
        Booking sekarang dan dapatkan teknisi terpercaya untuk kebutuhan Anda. Proses cepat, harga transparan.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href="/services"
          class="inline-flex h-12 min-w-[220px] items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white px-8 text-body font-semibold text-primary-700 shadow-sm transition-all duration-150 ease-out hover:bg-primary-50 hover:shadow-md focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-white"
        >
          Booking Sekarang
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex h-12 min-w-[220px] items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-primary-400 px-8 text-body font-medium text-primary-200 transition-all duration-150 ease-out hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-white focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-white"
        >
          Hubungi Kami
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
